@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/mixins/text.mixin"

.button
  height: 38px
  display: inline-block
  color: $black
  text-align: center
  vertical-align: middle
  -webkit-user-select: none
  -moz-user-select: none
  -ms-user-select: none
  user-select: none
  background-color: transparent
  border: 1px solid transparent
  padding: 12px 16px
  border-radius: 4px
  transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out, border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out
  @include text-button

  &.button-disabled
    color: $gray-4 !important
    background-color: $gray-2 !important
    border-color: $gray-2 !important

  &:focus,
  &:active
    outline: none

  &.button-primary
    color: $white
    background-color: $primary
    border-color: $primary

    &:hover
      color: $white
      background-color: $dark-primary
      border-color: $dark-primary


  &.button-secondary
    color: $gray-6
    background-color: $gray-1
    border-color: $gray-1

    &:hover
      color: $gray-6
      background-color: $gray-2
      border-color: $gray-2

  &.button-outline
    color: $primary
    background-color: transparent
    border-color: $light-primary

    &:hover
      color: $primary
      background-color: $light-primary
      border-color: $light-primary

    &.button-disabled
      color: $gray-3 !important
      background-color: transparent !important
      border-color: $gray-3 !important

  &.button-ghost
    color: $primary
    background-color: transparent
    border-color: transparent

    &:hover
      color: $dark-primary
      background-color: transparent
      border-color: transparent

    &.button-disabled
      color: $gray-3 !important
      background-color: transparent !important
      border-color: transparent !important

@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/mixins"

.checkbox-container
  position: relative
  cursor: pointer
  display: inline-flex
  margin: 0
  @include non-selectable()

  .checkbox
    position: fixed
    left: 99999px
    opacity: 0

    &:checked ~ .checkbox-content
      @include text-button

    &:checked ~ .checkbox-mark:after
      top: 2px
      left: 2px
      width: 10px
      height: 10px
      background-color: $primary

    &.checkbox-indeterminate ~ .checkbox-mark:after
      top: 5px
      left: 2px
      height: 4px
      width: 10px
      background-color: $primary

    &[disabled] ~ .checkbox-mark
      border: 1px solid $gray-2
      pointer-events: none
      cursor: default

    &[disabled]:checked ~ .checkbox-mark:after
      background-color: $gray-3

    &[disabled] ~ .checkbox-content
      opacity: .5


  .checkbox-mark
    position: absolute
    top: 0
    left: 0
    z-index: 2
    height: 16px
    width: 16px
    border: 1px solid $gray-3
    background-color: $white
    border-radius: 2px

    &:after
      content: ""
      position: absolute
      top: 4px
      left: 4px
      width: 6px
      height: 6px
      background: white
      border: 0
      transition: top 0.3s, left 0.3s, width 0.3s, height 0.3s


  .checkbox-content
    display: inline-block
    padding-left: 24px
    min-height: 16px
    @include text-label

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/mixins"

.radio-container
  position: relative
  cursor: pointer
  display: inline-flex
  margin: 0
  @include non-selectable()

  .radio
    position: fixed

    opacity: 0

    &:checked ~ .radio-content

    &[disabled] ~ .radio-mark

    left: 0

    height: 16px
    width: 16px
    border: 1px solid $gray-3
    background-color: $white
    border-radius: 50%

    &:after
      content: ""
      position: absolute
      top: 4px
      left: 4px
      width: 6px
      height: 6px
      border-radius: 50%
      background: white
      border: 0
      transition: top 0.2s, left 0.2s, width 0.2s, height 0.2s

    padding-left: 24px

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "src/sass/variables/colors.variable"
@import "src/sass/mixins/utilities.mixin"
@import "src/sass/mixins/text.mixin"

.switch-container
  position: relative
  cursor: pointer
  display: inline-flex
  margin: 0
  @include non-selectable()

  .switch
    position: fixed
    left: 99999px
    opacity: 0

    &:checked ~ .switch-toggle-bar
      background: $primary

    &:checked ~ .switch-toggle-bar .switch-toggle-thumb
      transform: translate3d(24px, 0, 0)

    &[disabled]:not(:checked) ~ .switch-toggle-bar
      background-color: $gray-2
      pointer-events: none
      cursor: default

    &[disabled]:checked ~ .switch-toggle-bar
      opacity: 0.5

    &[disabled] ~ .switch-content
      opacity: .5


  .switch-toggle-bar
    width: 48px
    height: 24px
    border-radius: 24px
    background: $gray-3
    margin-right: 16px
    transition: all 80ms linear
    transition-property: background-color
    transition-delay: 50ms

  .switch-toggle-thumb
    position: absolute
    z-index: 1
    width: 18px
    height: 18px
    background-color: $white
    border-radius: 50%
    top: 3px
    left: 3px
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0)
    transition: all 80ms linear
    transition-property: transform

  .switch-content
    color: $black
    @include text-h5()
